For the most of you reading this post it might be a small shock, but don't be alarmed. I also own a company with the same name which is going to stop this February.

After running this company for too long without real results, and ofcourse moving to my new job. I have decided that I will give up on this company so I can focus on personal projects and my job at Teemr

This being said, is still have some side projects which need to be finished, this will be done in the next week so I can go back to works with an empty mind, which should be very refreshing.
